import { Grid, List, ListItem, Typography } from "@mui/material";

const Expiriances = () => {
  return (
    <Grid container alignItems="baseline">
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="h6">Senior Software Engineer</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Perfectial/Avenga</Typography>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="body1">November 2021 - till present</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">Projects:</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">
          Cryptocurrency. Application cryptocurrency wallet, and trade
          cryptocurrency, cryptoWallet cryptocurrency. Exchange crypto for any
          money, real Estate.
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">Responsibilities:</Typography>
        <List
          sx={{
            width: "100%",
            maxWidth: 360,
            bgcolor: "background.paper",
            position: "relative",
            overflow: "auto",
            maxHeight: 300,
            "& ul": { padding: 0 },
          }}
        >
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              Bug fixing, add some functionality
            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              Communication with the customer's team
            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              Validation of multiple elements according to a specific criterion
            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              Writing new features with the existing UI toolkit
            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              Environment and Tools: React-Native, Redux, TypeScript, GraphQL,
              Git, Jira.
            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="h6">Senior Software Engineer</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Temy</Typography>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="body1">May 2021 – November 2021</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">Projects:</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">
          Intelligence Platform. The project is a cloud-based intelligence
          platform that empowers real estate professionals to attain predictable
          development, capital, and asset projects across real estate project
          types. It leverages the power of automation, data analytics, and
          proactive insights to help you make better and faster decisions on one
          complex project or several different portfolios.
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">Responsibilities:</Typography>
        <List
          sx={{
            width: "100%",
            maxWidth: 360,
            bgcolor: "background.paper",
            position: "relative",
            overflow: "auto",
            maxHeight: 300,
            "& ul": { padding: 0 },
          }}
        >
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>

          <ListItem>

          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              Environment and Tools: React-Native, Redux, TypeScript, GraphQL,
              Git, Jira.
            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="h6">Senior Software Engineer</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">LITSLINK</Typography>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="body1">June 2018 – April 2021</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">Projects:</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">E-system for technical support.</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">Responsibilities:</Typography>
        <List
          sx={{
            width: "100%",
            maxWidth: 360,
            bgcolor: "background.paper",
            position: "relative",
            overflow: "auto",
            maxHeight: 300,
            "& ul": { padding: 0 },
          }}
        >
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              Bug fixing, add some functionality
            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>

          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>

          <ListItem>

          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>

              Git, Jira, ASP.NET, Visual Basic, Node.js. MongoDB, Twilio,
              Angular, Rx.js.
            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="h6">Software Engineer</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Customertimes</Typography>

      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="body1">November 2017 – June 2018</Typography>

            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="h6">Senior Software Engineer</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Zazmic Inc.</Typography>

            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="h6">Software Engineer</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Sannacode</Typography>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="body1">August 2016 – April 2017</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">Projects:</Typography>

          Smart city application. Online application. The application taught the
          art of negotiations.
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">Responsibilities:</Typography>
        <List
          sx={{
            width: "100%",
            maxWidth: 360,
            bgcolor: "background.paper",
            position: "relative",
            overflow: "auto",
            maxHeight: 300,

        >

            </Typography>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="h6">Software Engineer</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Freelance</Typography>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6}>
        <Typography variant="body1">September 2015 – August 2016</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2">Projects:</Typography>
